### Test Webhook Endpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
x-paystack-signature: {{signature}}

{
  "event": "charge.success",
  "data": {
    "reference": "PAY_1234567890_ABC123",
    "amount": 5000,
    "currency": "KES",
    "status": "success"
  }
}

### Test Webhook with Failed Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
x-paystack-signature: {{signature}}

{
  "event": "charge.failed",
  "data": {
    "reference": "PAY_1234567890_DEF456",
    "amount": 5000,
    "currency": "KES",
    "status": "failed"
  }
}

### Variables (set these in your environment)
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
# @signature = your_webhook_signature_here 